      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, \"goblin raid\"? I'm not sure what you mean by that. I'm strictly looking at the demographic record and trying to understand the statistical anomalies in the census counts. Can you get back to the actual historical factors, like migration patterns or mortality rates, that would explain those population drops?",
